  <note type="content" displayLabel="Note">This collection includes materials accessioned as Mss. 4700.0887; A digital version of the transcript (pdf) exists for duplication purposes; A digital version of the audio recording (mp3) exists for duplication purposes and public access in the Special Collections Reading Room; Interview conducted by Rashada Jenkins.</note>
  <note type="biographical/historical" displayLabel="Biographical Note">Don Bradford committed himself to God at age 12 and recommited at age 21.  He founded the nondenominational Charity Christian Center Church in Baton Rouge, La., in 1985 and has served as its pastor.</note>
